name: Tiny Golden Sparrow Necklace (Gold Filled Chain)
description:
A tiny,sweet, gold vermeil sparrow glides on delicate 14k gold filled chain, and closes with a spring-ring clasp.

Simple. Sweet. Feminine.
Perfect for everyday, and to layer with other necklaces.

The tiny sparrow charm measures approximately 13 x 14 x 2mm (or about 1/2" at its widest point). Necklace measures about 16.5", and has a 2" extender chain with a swarovski crystal on the end.

Arrives in a beautiful organza drawstring pouch.

name: Fabric Yoyo Flower Necklace (Yellow/Pink)
description:
This asymmetrical necklace features a pretty yellow fabric yoyo flower, with shades of pink and olive green. It is hand wrapped to a strand of the most beautiful pink/cranberry faceted czech glass beads that have a slight bronze coating (which adds to the lovely vintage vibe!), and then attached to antique gold/brass rolo chain. Closes with a lobster clasp.

Perfect for spring and summer!

The fabric yoyo flower measures approximately 1", and the beads are 8mm in size. 

Note:  fabric yoyo flowers are unique, and may differ slightly from the one pictured, but be assured it will look very similar, and contain the same colors!

Necklace measures about 18.5" long.

Arrives in a pretty organza drawstring bag.

name: Cottage Roses - Handmade Tensha Bead Necklace (Frosted White with Blue Roses) on Extra Long Silver C
description:
The bead on this extra long necklace is a beautiful frosted white with blue roses outlined with gold detailing, tiny daisies and pretty olive green leaves. It is topped with pewter daisy spacers and a tiny light topaz swarovski crystal to bring out the daisies in the bead, and highlight the blue roses. The crystal adds just the right hint of sparkle.

Japanese Tensha bead measures 20mm round, and hangs from high-quality silver plated long and short chain (approximately 32" long), and closes with a lobster clasp.

This necklace can go dressy or casual and makes a pretty but subtle statement. The bead is extremely lightweight, so this is comfortable to wear, too! 

Your necklace will arrive in a pretty organza drawstring bag.

name: Perfect Union Necklace - Tiny Gold Filled Hammered Circle within a Tiny Sterling Silver Hammered Cir
description:
This sweet little necklace is perfect for everyday, and also to layer with other pieces.

A tiny hand-hammered gold filled circle (measuring about 8mm) sits inside a tiny but slightly bigger hand hammered sterling silver circle (measuring about 10mm). Strung on a delicate sterling silver chain - sweet and simple.

Necklace measures approximately 16.5" and comes with a 2" extender chain with a tiny swarovski crystal on the end, and closes with a sterling silver spring ring clasp.

Arrives in a beautiful organza drawstring pouch.

name: Springtime Necklace (Vintage Yellow Floral Cabochon Pendant on Pretty Silver Chain)
description:
This is the perfect necklace for Spring! 

A beautiful vintage (West Germany) floral cameo / cabochon (approximately 28mm in size) in a deep/bright yellow rests in a pretty silver plated setting. The yellow color highlights the floral bouquet (in shades of red, blue, white, and yellow) quite nicely!

Hangs from high-quality silver plated long and short chain (approximately 18"), and closes with a lobster clasp.


Arrives in a pretty organza drawstring pouch.
